thread.title: Mrs. E. Rake
thread.title_full: SkyLux Travel reviewed by Mrs. E. Rake

author: Mrs. E. Rake
title: Mrs. E. Rake
text:
I've worked Natalie twice now. I have to admit, I was a little skeptical the first time around due to reviews I'd read online. I did not have any issues with my tickets at all.
I've just booked a second trip through Natalie and SkyLux and I expect all will go smoothly.
Natalie is very responsive and prompt, she's patient and willing to work with any changes or requests I make.
I'm very happy with the service I've received.
